§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ The ❬span❭ of a set of vectors $v_1, …, v_k ∈ 𝗥^n$ is
    the set
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ \span(\set{v_1, …, v_k}) = \Set{α_1v_1 + ⋯ + α_kv_k}{α_i
        ∈ 𝗥}, ⦉
    ⦉
    the set of all linear combinations of the vectors $v_1, …,
    v_k$. ⦉
⦉

